<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Address {{#if isNewEmail}}Changed{{else}}Change Notification{{/if}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #007bff;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #007bff;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .highlight {
            background-color: #e8f4fd;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #007bff;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .email-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .security-notice {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            color: #856404;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .success-icon {
            color: #28a745;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        .warning-icon {
            color: #ffc107;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">{{systemName}}</div>
            <h1>{{#if isNewEmail}}‚úÖ Email Successfully Changed{{else}}‚ö†Ô∏è Email Change Notification{{/if}}</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello {{userName}},</p>

            {{#if isNewEmail}}
            <div class="highlight">
                <span class="success-icon">‚úÖ</span>
                <strong>Your email address has been successfully changed!</strong>
            </div>

            <p>This email confirms that your account email address has been updated on {{changeDate}} at {{changeTime}}.</p>

            <div class="email-details">
                <h3>New Email Address:</h3>
                <p><strong>{{newEmail}}</strong></p>
                <p><em>This is your new primary email for account notifications and login.</em></p>
            </div>

            <p>You can now use this email address to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Log into your account</li>
                <li>Receive system notifications</li>
                <li>Reset your password if needed</li>
                <li>Receive attendance reports and updates</li>
            </ul>

            {{else}}
            <div class="highlight">
                <span class="warning-icon">‚ö†Ô∏è</span>
                <strong>Your account email address is being changed.</strong>
            </div>

            <p>We're writing to inform you that the email address associated with your account was changed on {{changeDate}} at {{changeTime}}.</p>

            <div class="email-details">
                <h3>Email Change Details:</h3>
                <p><strong>Previous Email:</strong> {{oldEmail}}</p>
                <p><strong>New Email:</strong> {{newEmail}}</p>
                <p><strong>Changed On:</strong> {{changeDate}} at {{changeTime}}</p>
            </div>

            <p>If you initiated this change, no further action is required. A confirmation has also been sent to your new email address.</p>
            {{/if}}

            <div class="security-notice">
                <h3>üîí Security Notice</h3>
                <p><strong>If you did not request this email change:</strong></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Your account may have been compromised</li>
                    <li>Contact our support team immediately</li>
                    <li>Change your password as soon as possible</li>
                    <li>Review your recent account activity</li>
                </ul>
                <p><strong>Support Email:</strong> {{supportEmail}}</p>
            </div>

            {{#if isNewEmail}}
            <p>Thank you for keeping your account information up to date. If you have any questions or concerns, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
            {{else}}
            <p>This notification was sent to ensure the security of your account. Please keep this email for your records.</p>
            {{/if}}
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated security notification from {{systemName}}.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact us at {{supportEmail}}</p>
            <p><small>This email was sent on {{changeDate}} at {{changeTime}}</small></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
